---
title: Apple & Mint Slaw with Walnuts & Mustard Cider Dressing | Serves 2
description: This colourful slaw is super-charged in every way. Adding apple to our ready-to-go slaw mix gives a hint of sweetness, while the
mustard cider dressing adds flavour and softens everything up. Toasted walnuts make the perfect crunchy finish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/apple-mint-slaw-434754e8.jpg
